title: After-School Help for Students Tuesday through Friday this Fall (Historical Society of Pennsylvania)
text: ( Source : Historical Society of Pennsylvania ) HSP is pleased to announce the expansion of its student mentor program. HSP's Student Mentors are now available Tuesday through Friday after school to help students one-on-one with their research
